OL,3,C'No evidence of corruption or
OL,4,Cillegality' at Teesworks,
OL,5,Cinvestigation finds
OL,7,FA report, which was commissioned by
OL,8,FLevelling Up secretary Michael Gove
OL,9,Flast summer, found there was no
OL,10,Fevidence to support allegations of
OL,11,Fcorruption or illegality at the site.
OL,13,FHowever, the report did make 28
OL,14,Frecommendations, some of them around
OL,15,Ftransparency and governance.
OL,17,FIt also said the project needed to do
OL,18,Fmore to make sure taxpayers can see
OL,19,Fthat the investment is generating
OL,20,Fvalue for money.
