OL,3,C'No evidence of corruption or
OL,4,Cillegality' at Teesworks,
OL,5,Cinvestigation finds
OL,7,FThe 97-page report by an independent
OL,8,Fpanel, published on Monday, stated:
OL,9,F"Based on the information shared with
OL,10,Fthe panel, we have found no evidence
OL,11,Fto support allegations of corruption
OL,12,For illegality.
OL,14,F"However, there are issues of
OL,15,Fgovernance and transparency that need
OL,16,Fto be addressed and a number of
OL,17,Fdecisions taken by the bodies involved
OL,18,Fdo not meet the standards expected
OL,19,Fwhen managing public funds.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
