OL,7,F"The panel have therefore concluded
OL,8,Fthat the systems of governance and
OL,9,Ffinance in place within TVCA (the Tees
OL,10,FValley Combined Authority) and STDC
OL,11,F(the South Tees Development
OL,12,FCorporation) at present do not include
OL,13,Fthe expected sufficiency of
OL,14,Ftransparency and oversight across the
OL,15,Fsystem to evidence value for money."
