OL,5,Cinvestigation finds
OL,7,FResponding, Lord Houchen said: "The
OL,8,Fpeople of Teesside, Darlington and
OL,9,FHartlepool can welcome this
OL,10,Finvestigation, which sets out in black
OL,11,Fand white that there is no corruption
OL,12,For illegality at Teesworks.
OL,14,F"The investigation was thorough, wide-
OL,15,Franging, and detailed. It assessed
OL,16,Fmore than 1,400 documents, tens of
OL,17,Fthousands of pages of material and
OL,18,Fconducted 45 interviews, and I'd like
OL,19,Fto thank the panel for their hard work
OL,20,Fand diligence.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
