OL,7,F"I welcome the recommendations of the
OL,8,Fpanel, and my team and I are already
OL,9,Fworking to review the recommendations
OL,10,Fto improve our processes and
OL,11,Fprocedures in line with the report's
OL,12,Ffindings.
OL,14,F"It explicitly recognises that the
OL,15,FTeesworks Joint Venture was 'critical'
OL,16,Fin reaching an agreement with the Thai
OL,17,Fbanks and resolving the CPO, and that
OL,18,Fwithout them the progress we have seen
OL,19,Fwould not have been possible.
