OL,3,C'No evidence of corruption or
OL,4,Cillegality' at Teesworks,
OL,5,Cinvestigation finds
OL,7,FThe inquiry found the lack of
OL,8,Ftransparency surrounding the venture
OL,9,Fbetween the South Tees Development
OL,10,FCorporation and the companies run by
OL,11,Ftwo local developers has a "corrosive
OL,12,Feffect on public trust".
OL,14,FIt added a "high level" of
OL,15,Fconfidentiality around the transfer of
OL,16,Fownership to a 90-10 division of
OL,17,Fshares in favour of the private sector
OL,18,Fpartners in late 2021 "may be seen as
OL,19,Fan omission which has exacerbated the
OL,20,Fextent of public scepticism about the
OL,21,Fvalue for money of the project".
