OL,3,C'No evidence of corruption or
OL,4,Cillegality' at Teesworks,
OL,5,Cinvestigation finds
OL,7,FResponding in the House of Commons to
OL,8,Fthe report, Labour shadow communities
OL,9,Fminister Justin Madders said: "(The
OL,10,Freport) is damning. The issue has
OL,11,Falways been one of value for money,
OL,12,Fand on that, the report shows that
OL,13,Ftaxpayers' money was not being spent
OL,14,Fin the way the public should expect."
OL,16,FAfter quoting from the report, he
OL,17,Fsaid: "These are not minor trifling
OL,18,Fconcerns. They reveal a systemic and
OL,19,Fflawed decision-making process that
OL,20,Fhinders transparency and fails to show
OL,21,Fvalue for money.
