OL,3,C'No evidence of corruption or
OL,4,Cillegality' at Teesworks,
OL,5,Cinvestigation finds
OL,7,F"This scandal has exposed gaps in
OL,8,Faccountability and serious questions
OL,9,Fremain about the lack of local
OL,10,Fdemocratic scrutiny throughout this
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,F"It is now clearer than ever that this
OL,14,Fneeds to be investigated by the
OL,15,FNational Audit Office. It was an
OL,16,Fastonishing decision in the first
OL,17,Fplace for the Government to ignore the
OL,18,Fcalls for a fully independent
OL,19,Finvestigation into the serious
OL,20,Fallegations that have arisen, not just
OL,21,Ffrom the benches behind me."
